{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Scrap daylight savings time (DST) in the United Kingdom",
        "additional_details": "There have been a number of unsuccessful attempts in the UK Parliament to make changes to the current system, however it is time to change that and fully support this petition and initiative to scrap daylight savings time (DST) once and for all. I fully believe that the UK can lead the revolution and other countries that also support and adopt DST may follow suit.",
        "background": "Scrap daylight savings time (DST) in the United Kingdom and fix the time to either GMT/UTC or BST/UTC+1.",
